				],
				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Kithrak Voss, the knight hunting Lae'zel, rides in on a dragon and kills flaming fist on a bridge. Lae'zel approaches, thinking he might lead her to a creche, where she can bec ured of the tadpole.\n\nSVoss is spoiled, intelligent, and creepily calm and fatherly: Joaquin Phoenix in Gladiator. Smarmy and evil sounding. Pronunciation: Qudenos = cue-DAY-noss. Ghaik = GAYK. Kith'rak = KITH-rack. Lae'zel = lay-ZELL. Vlaakith = VLAH-kith."
				}
			}
